                                FixFonts

        FixFonts should be used after you have added or deleted fonts from
your Fonts drawer. (The Fonts drawer does not have an icon associated with
it; you have to use the Show All Files form the pull down menu item in
order to see the Fonts drawer on the Workbench.)

        With a floppy disk system, the only font immediately available to
you is Topaz. Topaz is stored in ROM. Other fonts are available in the
Fonts drawer on the AmigaFonts x.x disk, but to copy them to your Workbench
x.x disk, you would have to delete information from the disk to make room
for them.


